sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Code / KFP
    participant Exp as AI4RAGExperiment
    participant MPS as ModelsPreSelector
    participant GAM as GAMOptimizer
    participant RAG as SimpleRAG
    participant Chunker as LangChainChunker
    participant Chroma as ChromaVectorStore<br/>(in-memory)
    participant OGX as OGX Server<br/>HTTPS / TLS<br/>API Key Auth
    participant Eval as UnitxtEvaluator
    participant EH as EventHandler

    Note over User,EH: Phase 1: Models Pre-Selection (MPS)

    User->>Exp: search(benchmark_data, search_space)
    Exp->>MPS: pre_select(models, sample_data)
    MPS->>Chunker: chunk documents
    Chunker-->>MPS: chunked documents

    loop For each embedding model candidate
        MPS->>OGX: POST embeddings.create<br/>HTTPS / TLS / API Key
        OGX-->>MPS: embedding vectors
        MPS->>Chroma: store embeddings (in-memory)
    end

    loop For each foundation model candidate
        MPS->>Chroma: retrieve relevant chunks
        Chroma-->>MPS: retrieved documents
        MPS->>OGX: POST chat.completions.create<br/>HTTPS / TLS / API Key
        OGX-->>MPS: generated answers
        MPS->>Eval: evaluate(predictions, references)
        Eval-->>MPS: scores (correctness, faithfulness)
    end

    MPS-->>Exp: top model pairs ranked by score

    Note over User,EH: Phase 2: Full HPO with GAM Optimizer

    Exp->>OGX: POST vector_stores.create<br/>HTTPS / TLS / API Key
    OGX-->>Exp: vector_store_id

    Exp->>GAM: initialize(search_space, n_random_nodes)

    loop For each optimization iteration
        GAM->>Exp: next parameter combination (RAG Pattern)
        Exp->>EH: emit(pattern_started)

        Exp->>RAG: execute(pattern, benchmark_data)

        RAG->>Chunker: chunk documents
        Chunker-->>RAG: chunked documents

        RAG->>OGX: POST embeddings.create<br/>HTTPS / TLS / API Key
        OGX-->>RAG: embedding vectors

        RAG->>OGX: POST vector_io.insert<br/>HTTPS / TLS / API Key
        OGX-->>RAG: indexed

        par For each query (ThreadPoolExecutor, 10 threads)
            RAG->>OGX: POST vector_io.query<br/>HTTPS / TLS / API Key
            OGX-->>RAG: retrieved documents
            RAG->>OGX: POST chat.completions.create<br/>HTTPS / TLS / API Key
            OGX-->>RAG: generated answer
        end

        RAG-->>Exp: predictions + contexts

        Exp->>Eval: evaluate(predictions, references)
        Eval-->>Exp: scores with confidence intervals

        Exp->>GAM: update(pattern, scores)
        Exp->>EH: emit(pattern_completed, results)
    end

    Exp->>EH: emit(experiment_completed, all_results)
    EH-->>User: aggregated results (best RAG Pattern)
